snippet.title: GameDevHQ
snippet.description:
Welcome to GameDevHQ! Your one-stop shop for all things game development. We offer content every week focusing on new Unity C# Tutorials, Unity Art Pipeline Tutorials like Level Design and making things look awesome in Unity, and then we also have weekly game development news content. If you're new to Unity, or if you're an avid user, check us out at GameDevHQ.com and join our community where we have taught over 40,000 students how to make games and get careers with Unity! We've partnered with Unity to develop a series of Authorized Unity Courses and if you're interested in checking them out, go to GameDevHq.com 

We look forward to helping you reach your goals!

Hit that subscribe button, and join us on Discord. We can't wait to meet you!

Best,

GameDevHQ Team (Jonathan, Al, Ryan)
